---
name: legate.dispatch
description: "Mini-legate's new-work-launch skill. Runs on every heartbeat after babysit/merge/cleanup, independent of their state — consults `smithy status`, syncs the default branch, and launches workers on ready slices that have no in-flight worker yet. Triggers: heartbeat ticks, operator request for any planning verb (`/smithy.render`, `/smithy.mark`, `/smithy.cut`) or `/smithy.forge`, slice-merge events that unblock the next step. Skip for managing existing PRs (that's `legate.babysit`). Operators can disable this skill on repos where the conductor should only manage existing PRs."
